lamic teachings and values.   Honors and Awards  LUMS National Outreach Program S                                                                                                     (Aug 2017)  • Got admitted to LUMS with 120% scholarship on the basis of excellent academic and extracurricular achievements.  Merit Scholarship Award – Superior Group of Colleges                                                                    (Aug 2015)  • Awarded 100% Merit Scholarship for Intermediate based on outstanding academic performance in Matriculation.  2nd Position in Inter-school Mathematics Olympiad (ISMO)                                                             (Mar 2011)  • Achieved 2nd position out of 1600 participants twice in the PakTurk ISMO competition in Peshawar.                                                                                                                                                                      Skills  • Soft Skills:  Leadership, Problem-solving, Adaptability, Time Management, Teamwork, Written & Verbal Communication • Hard Skills: B2B Sales, LinkedIn Sales Navigator, CrunchBase, HubSpot, Research, Data Analysis, Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, PowerPoint), Canva, Adobe Photoshop 

